title: Cyberpunk 2077 Phantom Liberty: First Big Expansion Revealed! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 09.06.22
description:
Blessing and Greg talk about if Cyberpunk 2077's new expansion is enough to bring the game back, more God of War gameplay showing off a new realm, and fun Ubisoft leaks!

00:00:00 - Start
00:03:38 - Housekeeping

Football season is here and Andy and Mike are excited to be your play-by-play announcers for the Niners season. Your favorite gaming personalities are scattered all throughout the league! Be a part of Team KF on the Niners or join another team in the league in hopes to stop our chances at winning the championship. Find out how on today's stream after KFGD

The Roper Report  -
